headline: Meet the Construction Stock That's Quietly Crushing the Market (And Sees More Growth Ahead in 2025)
summary: Trane Technologies (NYSE: TT) is quietly having a fantastic year.  It has benefited from strong demand for its climate solutions products, especially in the commercial construction market.  The company is well-positioned for another strong year in 2025.
